query: COPY (SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP()) AS ctime, a.schemaname, a.relname, a.indexrelname, idx_scan, idx_tup_read, idx_tup_fetch, idx_blks_read, idx_blks_hit FROM pg_stat_all_indexes a, pg_statio_all_indexes b WHERE a.indexrelid = b.indexrelid) TO STDOUT (FORMAT CSV, HEADER);

COPY (SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP()) AS ctime, datname, numbackends, xact_commit, xact_rollback, blks_read, blks_hit, tup_returned, tup_fetched, tup_inserted, tup_updated, tup_deleted FROM pg_stat_database) TO STDOUT (FORMAT CSV, HEADER);
